Description: I grew up with my parents driving this stretch of road between Walpole and Denmark. The road is too narrow for the high speeds, and the bends in the forested areas are dangerous. This is coupled with the issue of the road being a high tourist traffic area, being a wine region. During the holiday months, a high load of tourist traffic (including caravans) use the area, many of whom are unaware of how to drive to conditions.
